# ScholarMCP README 规范 / README Rules / README規則

## 规则 / Rules / 規則

- 每个模块/服务必须包含README.md文件。
- Every module/service must include a README.md file.

- README需包含：简介、用法、API说明、安装/运行方法、许可证等。
- README should include: introduction, usage, API description, setup/run instructions, license, etc.

- 推荐多语言（中英日）文档。
- Multilingual (Chinese, English, Japanese) documentation is recommended.
